<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:12:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登呼吁对“钢城”匹兹堡的中国金属征收更高关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-call-higher-tariffs-chinese-metals-steel-city-pittsburgh-2024-04-17/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三将呼吁对中国金属产品大幅提高关税，这是旨在取悦摇摆州宾夕法尼亚州钢铁工人的一揽子政策的一部分，但此举可能会激怒北京。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-call-higher-tariffs-chinese-metals-steel-city-pittsburgh-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商一汽汽车金融部门推出无首付贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-faws-auto-finance-unit-launches-loan-with-no-down-payment-2024-04-17/</link><description>中国国有汽车制造商一汽集团的汽车金融部门推出了无首付贷款计划，成为自政府取消最低还款额以来首批采取此举措的供应商之一。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:04:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-faws-auto-finance-unit-launches-loan-with-no-down-payment-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车将与小鹏汽车合作推出新架构以降低中国电动汽车成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-roll-out-new-architecture-with-xpeng-cut-china-ev-costs-2024-04-17/</link><description>大众汽车周三表示，它已与中国合作伙伴小鹏汽车开发了一种新的智能电动汽车架构，这家德国汽车制造商表示，这将有助于其在其最大的市场上提供更实惠的电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:47:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-roll-out-new-architecture-with-xpeng-cut-china-ev-costs-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国担忧加剧，日本公司再次向美国发起进攻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-inc-makes-renewed-us-push-china-fears-mount-2024-04-17/</link><description>由于对中国需求和北京对供应链影响力的担忧促使日本企业明显转向全球最大经济体，因此越来越多的日本企业将其增长计划转向美国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:14:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-inc-makes-renewed-us-push-china-fears-mount-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国田协承诺在半程马拉松惨败后采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/chinas-federation-promises-action-after-half-marathon-debacle-2024-04-17/</link><description>周日北京半程马拉松的视频显示，三名选手似乎放慢速度，以便让中国选手何洁超越他们并获胜，中国田径协会（CAA）誓言加强对其路跑赛事的监管。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:58:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/chinas-federation-promises-action-after-half-marathon-debacle-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，万科寻求出售物流运营商普洛斯的股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-seeks-offload-stake-logistics-operator-glp-bloomberg-reports-2024-04-17/</link><description>据彭博社周三报道，万科正寻求出售其在物流公司普洛斯的全部股份，因为这家现金短缺的国有房地产开发商希望提高流动性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-seeks-offload-stake-logistics-operator-glp-bloomberg-reports-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾和美军将在联合演习中训练夺回岛屿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-forces-train-retaking-island-joint-military-drills-2024-04-17/</link><description>随着马尼拉将重点转向外部防御，菲律宾和美国军队将于下周开始在面向台湾和南中国海的地区举行联合军事演习，模拟夺回敌占岛屿的情况。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-forces-train-retaking-island-joint-military-drills-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国军方计划在缅甸边境附近举行更多演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-plans-more-drills-near-myanmar-border-2024-04-17/</link><description>官方媒体称，中国将从周三开始在中缅边境附近举行防空和实弹演习，这是本月第二轮此类演习，因为缅甸执政军政府和叛军之间的战斗加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:16:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-plans-more-drills-near-myanmar-border-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国和亚洲盟友推动成立新小组来监督朝鲜制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-asia-allies-push-new-panel-monitor-north-korea-sanctions-2024-04-17/</link><description>三名消息人士周三表示，在俄罗斯和中国阻挠联合国的监测活动后，美国、韩国和日本正在推动成立一个新的多国专家小组（可能在联合国之外），以确保对朝鲜的制裁得到执行。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:12:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-asia-allies-push-new-panel-monitor-north-korea-sanctions-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>ASML第一季度订单未达预期，但中国销量保持增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-reports-q1-earnings-13-billion-worse-than-expected-new-bookings-2024-04-17/</link><description>计算机芯片制造商最大的设备供应商阿斯麦周三报告称，第一季度新订单低于预期，尽管在美国主导的限制下，对中国的销售仍保持不变。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:07:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-reports-q1-earnings-13-billion-worse-than-expected-new-bookings-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国派战斗机在台湾海峡跟踪美国海军飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navy-patrol-plane-flies-through-taiwan-strait-2024-04-17/</link><description>中国军方周三表示，已派出战斗机对飞越敏感的台湾海峡的美国海军巡逻机进行监视和警告，这一任务是在中美防长通话几小时后进行的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:00:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navy-patrol-plane-flies-through-taiwan-strait-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚计划斥资 320 亿美元加强国防建设，导弹、无人机和军舰成为首要任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/missiles-drones-warships-priority-australia-plans-32-bln-defence-boost-2024-04-17/</link><description>澳大利亚将在未来十年增加国防开支 503 亿澳元（合 320 亿美元），并调整其武器计划，以重点发展导弹、无人机和军舰，以应对中美之间爆发太平洋冲突的可能性</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 04:29:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/missiles-drones-warships-priority-australia-plans-32-bln-defence-boost-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪推出三款越野防城宝新车型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-unveils-three-new-models-its-off-road-fangchengbao-lineup-2024-04-17/</link><description>随着中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪加大力度进军高价细分市场，比亚迪以其高端品牌方成宝推出了三款新车型，其中包括两款概念车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 03:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-unveils-three-new-models-its-off-road-fangchengbao-lineup-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国国防部长表示，中美应找到发展务实军事关系的途径</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-should-find-ways-pragmatic-military-relations-chinese-defence-minister-2024-04-17/</link><description>中国国防部长周三表示，中美两国应探讨发展两军务实合作关系，“逐步积累互信”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 01:08:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-should-find-ways-pragmatic-military-relations-chinese-defence-minister-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛选举投票受到中美关注，以影响地区安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-votes-election-watched-by-china-us-regional-security-impact-2024-04-16/</link><description>所罗门群岛周三举行议会选举，这是自 2022 年总理玛纳西·索加瓦雷 (Manasseh Sogavare) 与中国达成安全协议以来的首次选举，拉近了这个太平洋岛国与北京的距离。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 23:11:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-votes-election-watched-by-china-us-regional-security-impact-2024-04-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>